query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `design_service_life_values` (
	`id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
	`componentCode` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
	`componentName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
	`buildingClass` enum('class_a','class_b','class_c','all') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'all',
	`propertyType` varchar(100),
	`designServiceLife` int NOT NULL,
	`minServiceLife` int,
	`maxServiceLife` int,
	`bestCaseServiceLife` int,
	`worstCaseServiceLife` int,
	`dataSource` varchar(255),
	`notes` text,
	`isActive` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
	`companyId` int,
	`createdBy` int,
	`createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	`updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	INDEX `idx_dsl_component` (`componentCode`),
	INDEX `idx_dsl_building_class` (`buildingClass`),
	INDEX `idx_dsl_property_type` (`propertyType`),
	INDEX `idx_dsl_company` (`companyId`)
);
